Vipont Laboratories Incsaid the Canadian Bureau of Non-Prescription Drugs approved itsViadent toothpaste and oral rinse for marketing.    The company also said it finalized an agreement with aCanadian marketing company to introduce the product in thecountry. It said Viadent helps prevent plaque build-up andinflamed gums.    The products should be available in Canada in three to fourmonths, the company added. Reuter&#3;